{"word":"G4028 - περικαλύπτω - perikalýptō - per-ee-kal-oop'-to - Blindfold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περικαλύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">perikalýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-kal-oop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blindfold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மூடு, கட்டு, பொதிந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to cover all around to cover up, cover over"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2572 - καλύπτω - kalýptō - kal-oop'-to/2572\">G2572</a>; to <i>cover</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>entirely</i> (the face, a surface): - blindfold, cover, overlay.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}